            <br /><br />
            I very much enjoyed this game as a kid, and decided to try and make my own game like it.
            <br /> <br />

            <h4>Gameplay</h4>
            Treds will try to keep to that simple gameplay. The camera moves in one direction at a time, and only moves forward with the player. The player can move, rotate their turret, and shoot.
            <br /><br />
            
            <h4>Art</h4>
            My goal with this was also to make my own art for everything. Trax was largely made in 8x8 and 16x16 bit sizes, all in greyscale.
